{"tid":1347084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗一疫文宣方向建議","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:47:28.000Z","uid":65072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12f723a5c37bfeca2919dccd6021c88c582ce7fc","tid":1347084,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"我地善智不善力<br />\n黑幫善力不善智<br />\n<br />\n硬碰絕非上策, 以下係我文宣建議<br />\n在文宣玩大佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察無能</span></span>, <br />\n縱容暴徒打平民<br />\n明明有晒相, 有埋名, 有片, 人證物證<br />\n警察無為令全港堪入恐慌, 人人自危<br />\n打人暴徒宵搖法外, 隨時出現在你我身邊<br />\n令自身, 家人, 朋友隨時受性命威脅<br />\n無辜事民, 大肚婆也被牽連其中受傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 全民抗暴 </span></span><br />\n警察放生暴徒, 四處破壞香港<br />\n拯救香港, 人人有責<br />\n要將班人, 親朋變過街老鼠<br />\n19區大字報貼晒班人資料<br />\n全港人認住班暴徒, <br />\n暴徒出現在身邊, 要認出來遠離之<br />\n行到邊都俾人認到<br />\n俾人指指點點<br />\n破壞香港法治既債係要還<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迫政府做野</span></span><br />\n當全港人都迫政府拉人<br />\n去到邊都俾人問幾時拉人<br />\n還我安寧香港<br />\n不能讓這事石沉大海<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民賤聯狼狽為奸</span></span><br />\n何妖有份牽涉其中<br />\n票債票償<br />\n踢走支持暴徒團體<br />\n人人有責<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次係機會俾全港市民落水<br />\n人唔理政治, 政治嚟搵你<br />\n警察靠唔住<br />\n人人都可以出力守護香港<br />\n上面有咩可以更好更有效<br />\n歡迎大家提出<br />\n鬥力不及黑社會<br />\n鬥智我哋一定贏<br />\n文宣一定要打好<br />\n<br />\n兄弟互勉之"},{"pid":"39a16d403d7d0d673c99d22a2b6307021e2c967b","tid":1347084,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"班暴徒係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港版鄭捷</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為警察無能, 鄭捷可能隨時在你我, 家人, 朋友身邊出現"},{"pid":"107df57bbde39e7d3f70b2809d65a1105b9e3910","tid":1347084,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"港警淪為第三世界級數<br />\n比菲警更無能<br />\n有晒樣,名,證據都唔拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d1a75e2204e8ae16bafd21759ebeeb9284717c","tid":1347084,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:32:25.000Z","msg":"電視媒體唔可靠<br />\n靠大家fb ig還原事件真相"},{"pid":"a697b7d4b226a25bbe6f8ac575d439bce463e704","tid":1347084,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:36:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你想香港被黑社會統治嗎</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6941888c98ac7e6225fdbfa38d80083e86c8eaa1","tid":1347084,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"不要期望警察能保護市民生命財產安全<br />\n他們看不見暴徒手上的武器<br />\n999會Cut線<br />\n他們沒有手錶看時間<br />\n他們會在報警後一小時才到場"},{"pid":"5c7e51d4033a97a9e30542f58b77b966f462b700","tid":1347084,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跟返自己生日月份，睇返搵邊個講元朗既事</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>【一月、二月】 David R. Stilwell</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/biographies/david-r-stilwell/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fbiographies%2Fdavid-r-stilwell%2F&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=6148c02e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/biographies/david-r-stilwell/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【三月】 Mitch McConnell</strong><br />\nEmail：senator@mcconnell.senate.gov<br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mcconnellpress\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmcconnellpress&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=fb736098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mcconnellpress</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【四月】 Nancy Patricia Pelosi</strong><br />\nEmail：<a href=\"https://pelosi.house.gov